            "title": "滬指開市跌10點 深成指跌84點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市初段向下，上證綜指以4074點開市，跌10點或0.25%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開市報14897點，亦跌84點或0.56%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數跌16點或0.35%，開報4751點；創業板指數開市報3660點，跌28點或0.77%。</p>\n</div>",
